snippet.textDisplay: Dear Brother, Ameen Sum Ameen I should be destroyed if I am wrong. Jahan tuk Darood ka taluq hai to hamarey nabi ko kiya rutba Allah Tala ney diya hai key Quraan main furma diya key Aey momino tum bhi in per Darood bhejo key main bhi in per Darood bhejta hoon. Meri koi aisi namaz nahi hoti jiskey baad main hath utha ker sirf apni dua kerta hoon her namaz key baad hath utha ker dua key bajaey sirf Darood e Ibrahimi perhta hoon or is ki fazilat sey hi Allah meri jaiz hajaton ko poora kerta hai. Ab baat reh gai key wo hamari Darood ba nafsey nafees khud suntey hain to aisa nahi hai. Ek Hadis main hai key agar koi momin mujh per darood bhejta hai to Allah Tala apney fazal sey foran ek Farishta peda ker deta hai jo Aap tak ye darood forum puhancha deta hai. Kiya is sahi hadis key baad bhi aap ye kena pasand karengey key hamarey aqa  darood khud suntey hain. Main sirf ek hi baat kahoonga key hum tamam musalman Asian countries main intahai jahiliat ka shikar hain or is ki sub sey bari waja Quraan or Hadis sey doori hai or is doori ki waja hamarey molvis or peer hazraat hain jo nahi chahtey key ek aam musalman deen sey agahi hasil karey. Agar hum log apney deen sey agahi karengey to in Khabees molvi or peeron ko kon ghans daley ga in ki rozi roti band hojaigi. Is sey ziayada simple tareeqey sey main koi baat nahi samjha sakta hoo. Asian contries main sirf SHIRK or BIDDAAT sey bharey hoey aqaid hain jo hamari nasloon ko chat jaiga or hum sift kuth putly jaisey musalman hongey jin main Iman nahi hoga or yahi Yahood o Nasara chahtey hain key hum sirf naam key musalman reh jain takey phir koi Sultan Salahuddin na peda hosakey. History ko study karengey to sub samjh main ajaiga. Hamarey Profit ney Fatah Macca key baad sub sey pehla hokum diya tha key tamam Mazar toor dalo or pakki qabron ko musmar ker do, Kiya ye hukum hum tak aaj tak kisi molvi or kisi peer ney puhanchaya?? Agar puhancha detey to kia Pakistan main Qabar parasti hoti??? Un mazaron per jo jahil log shirk kertey hain kiya aisa kertey?? Main khud ek bara mazar parust tha lekin jub sey Allah ney hidayat ki roshni sey nawaza hai to mera bus nahi chalta key sub mazaron ko torh daloon kiyun key ye ek mafia key under hai jin ka deen iman sirf paisa hai. Merey bhai agar deen main in mazaron ka hokum hota to Pakistan main jitney oliya key mazar hain unsey rutbey main kahin ziada barey Sahaba karam ki kachi qabren Saudiya main na hoti. Saudi Arab main sirf mazar hi mazar hotey. Roz e mehshar Allah Tala apney bandon main sey jiskey chahey sub gunnah maaf ker dega ager nahi maaf karega to Shirk nahi maaf karey ga. (Quraan)Shaitan hum ko hamarey burey kaam hamari nazron main acha ker key dikhata hai (Quraan) Agar hum apney burey kaamon ko Shatan ki wajah sey acha samjhney lagen to phir shatan kamyab or hum jahannam main... Apney her kaam ko jo hum kertey hain unko Quraan, Hadis or Sahaba karam ki zindagiun main talash Karen agar in main sey kisi main wo mojood hai to Karen werna chordena hi behter hoga. Hamrey liye sirf or sirf hamarey Aqa Hazrat Muhammad (PHUH) ki zaat hi rehnuma or laiq e Taqleed honi chahiye na key aaj kal key nam niha molvi or peer hazrat. Socho key agar hum maghrib ki namaz 3 rakat key bajai 4 rikaat furz purh lein to is main kiya harj hai ziyada tilawat ziyada sajdey or ziyada rakoo sey kia hamen maghrib ki namz 4 rikaat ka sawab ziyada milna chahiye?? Nahi hergiz nahi kiyun key ye Aap Salm ka bataya hoa tareeqa nahi hai is liye sawab ki bajai bai sey gunnah hojaigi wo namaz jo Aap Salm key tareeqey sey nahi parhi jaigi. Isi ek choti si missal sey samajh len key hamari aaj ki dunya or hamarey aamal kiya AAP key bataye hoe tareeon per hai?? Nahi hergiz nahi, to phir hum kahan bhutak rahey hai??? Khudara is shatani jaal ko samjhen or Quraan or Hadis ko study Karen or Pakistan main horehey her shirkiya kaamon sey khud ko or apney ahlo ayal or doston ko bachain, Shaid hamari koshishon sey ek bhi insaan jahannam ki bharakti hoi aag sey bach gaya to us key nek amaal main hamara bhi hissa hoga (Insha Allah). Her us cheez or amal ko turk kerden jo Quraan or Hamarey Aqa key derbar sey stamped na ho. Sirf itna bhejey main betha len key Hamarey Rasool Salm ney hamen her acha amal bata ker gain hain jo hamen Jahannam sey bachata hei or Jannat ki taraf le jata hai. Agar phir bhi koi amal aap ko buhat acha lagey or wo hamarey aqa key derbar sey stamped na ho yani un ki hadis main na miley to us amal ko tark kerden chahey jitna bhi acha lagey, werna soch len key shaid Nauzibillah wo hamen ye acha amal batana bhool gai hai, Hamen apna rehber or Qaid sirf or sirf Rasool Akram (PBUH) ko hi manna chahiye na key aaj key molvi or peeron ko. Allah hamen Quraan or Ahadis ki sahi sajh ata fermai (Ameen)
